04:28.602 --> 04:30.104
- SO WHAT NOW?

04:30.104 --> 04:32.481
- WHAT DO YOU MEAN,
"SO WHAT NOW?"

04:32.481 --> 04:33.816
I'M MARRIED.

04:33.816 --> 04:35.651
- UH-HUH.

04:35.651 --> 04:37.445
- JESUS.
[phone rings]

04:37.445 --> 04:39.571
YOU'RE SUCH A FUCKING ASSHOLE.

04:41.865 --> 04:43.451
HEY, MICKEY.
- OH, MICKEY MILKOVICH?

04:43.451 --> 04:44.493
