WITH THE NUT WARD TALK.

07:02.465 --> 07:04.132
HE'LL GET HIS SHIT STRAIGHT.

07:04.132 --> 07:05.510
HE'LL BRING THE KID BACK.

07:07.386 --> 07:08.637
HE WILL.

07:22.568 --> 07:24.570
- HI.
UH, OKAY.

07:24.570 --> 07:27.531
