WITH A "K"?

07:27.531 --> 07:29.032
OKAY, YOU CAN STAY.

07:29.032 --> 07:31.493
AND THEN CARLSON WITH A "C,"
YOU ARE ACTUALLY

07:31.493 --> 07:33.579
