- YEAH.

07:37.667 --> 07:38.709
- OKAY.

07:38.709 --> 07:41.962
- [muffled moaning]

07:41.962 --> 07:43.589
- EXCUSE ME.
- YEAH?

07:43.589 --> 07:45.757
- YOU'RE THE RESIDENT ASSISTANT
ON THIS FLOOR, RIGHT?

07:45.757 --> 07:49.177
- UH-HUH.
- I'M KAREN PERLOW'S MOM--417?

