UNDER THAT WOULD BE

08:46.276 --> 08:47.903
LIKE STEPPING ON A GRAPE.

08:47.903 --> 08:49.655
- MY NEW ROOMMATE
FROM CRAIGSLIST

08:49.655 --> 08:50.989
