THAT TIME OF MONTH.

09:25.691 --> 09:27.609
- TOUCH MY CART,
I'LL CALL THE COPS.

09:27.609 --> 09:31.154
- I WAS JUST ADMIRING
YOUR ORGANIZATIONAL SKILL.

09:31.154 --> 09:33.448
YOU'RE A WONDER.
- GET A JOB, FRANK.

09:33.448 --> 09:35.325
