CHURCH-GOING BUDDIES

09:42.708 --> 09:45.127
THE GREAT PRIVILEGE
OF SUPPORTING ME AND MINE.

09:45.127 --> 09:46.753
[laughs]

09:46.753 --> 09:50.465
