GET READY FOR SCHOOL.

11:23.809 --> 11:25.310
- SCHOOL DOESN'T START
FOR TWO MORE DAYS.

11:25.310 --> 11:26.853
- YEAH, MIDDLE SCHOOL
STARTS IN TWO DAYS.

11:26.853 --> 11:28.856
HIGH SCHOOL STARTS TOMORROW.

11:28.856 --> 11:30.857
