OF HIGH SCHOOL?

11:30.857 --> 11:35.445
OH, SWEETIE, ARE YOU SCARED?
- NO.

11:35.445 --> 11:37.197
- I HATED NINTH GRADE.

11:37.197 --> 11:40.867
